title: DC Comics Justice League Action Batmobile and Batjet Vehicle
feature: Signature Batmobile featuring new Justice League Action deco
Batmobile morphs into high speed flight mode Batjet
Includes exclusive Batman mini figure with pop off joints for mix-and-match play with other DC mini figures (sold separately)
Vehicle has a side-mounted blaster that fires projectiles
Perfect addition to any Batman collection
description: Speed to the Gotham City crime scene in this signature Batmobile featuring new Justice League Action deco, a slick black body, silvery rims and a side-mounted blaster that fires projectiles from the hood! When the wings come out, the Batmobile also morphs into high speed flight mode to become the Batjet! Includes an exclusive Batman mini figure with pop off joints for mix-and-match play with other DC mini figures. Other figures sold separately, subject to availability. By Mattel
